ive Thinkers for a Post-Anthropocene<\\/strong><\\/p><p>A talk by the artist-designer Fara Peluso showing how art and design can be mediators between science and the public to build a collective memory.<\\/p><p>More info: <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lacunalab.org\\/events\\/comprehensive-thinkers-for-a-post-anthropocene\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/lacunalab.org\\/events\\/comprehensive-thinkers-for-a-post-anthropocene<\\/a><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><em>25 February 7 pm to 28 February 11 pm<\\/em><\\/p><p>Nayeli Vega Vargas, Thomas Heidtmann, Ambika Joshi | <strong>K(not) a Conversation<\\/strong><\\/p><p>K(not) a Conversation&nbsp;is an installation exploring the concepts of artificial intelligence, creativity and labour. Inspired by ancient indigenous communication systems of Quipu knots, it instigates a communication and reflection process through the use of knots and AI systems.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>More info: coming soon<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><em>25 March 7 pm to 25 March 8 pm (tbc)<\\/em><\\/p><p>Thomas Heidtmann | <strong>slideedge.io \\u2013 digital inauguration<\\/strong><\\/p><p>slideedge.io constitutes an artistic framework which unites interactive sculptural installations with a dynamically generated virtual layer. During Vorspiel a digital prototype is presented to introduce the project to the public.<\\/p><p>More info: coming soon<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":null}','{\"external_participants\":[{\"name\":\"Ambika Joshi\",\"url\":null}],\"links\":[{\"title\":\"Facebook Event\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/events\\/846522596199943\"}]}',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1945,2138,'events','47','{\"id\":\"47\",\"status\":\"draft\",\"sort\":null,\"created_by\":\"14\",\"created_on\":\"2021-01-25 17:43:39\",\"modified_by\":\"14\",\"modified_on\":\"2021-01-26 11:16:35\",\"title\":\"Snapshot\",\"url\":\"snapshot\",\"start_date\":\"2021-01-25 19:00:00\",\"end_date\":null,\"cover\":\"83\",\"short_description\":\"Nu\\u00f1o de la Serna present a series of film interviews that reflect